        "created_at": "2023-05-09T07:06:08.618Z",
        "cooked": "<p>A while back a contact of mine removed their Signal account. They were member of several groups, yet their group membership was retained, despite them not having a Signal account anymore. As an admin of said groups this put me into an awkward position where I had to remove this person from the groups, making it appear as if I were kicking them out.</p>\n<p>What I think really should happen is that prior to removal of a Signal account the account is removed from all groups it‚Äôs a member of. Could this be looked at?</p>",
