        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/ba9def/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2023-05-09T09:24:04.455Z",
        "cooked": "<p>what is <code>removed their Signal account</code>? (see <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/difference-not-clear-between-delete-account-and-deregister-phone-number/18901\" class=\"inline-onebox\">Difference not clear between delete account and deregister phone number</a>)</p>\n<p>As for now <code>removed from all groups it‚Äôs a member of</code> is working as intended:</p><aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"135\" data-topic=\"18811\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/greyson-signal/48/2005_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/beta-feedback-for-the-upcoming-android-5-0-release/18811/135\">Beta feedback for the upcoming Android 5.0 release</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/beta-feedback/android-beta-feedback/97\"><span data-category-id=\"97\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #0088CC; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF; --parent-category-badge-color: #0088CC;\" data-parent-category-id=\"25\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --has-parent\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Android Beta Feedback</span></span></a>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Yeah, we accidentally forgot to take that string out. Initially we were going to manually leave all groups as part of the process, but that means other clients would be spammed with leave messages, so we decided against it until we could figure out a better way. Instead, we just rely on the fact that other clients safely ignore sending to unregistered users. For GV2 groups, admins can delete unregistered users when appropriate.\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n\n<p>imho<br>\na) if you only deregister (Settings ‚Üí Privacy ‚Üí Advanced ‚Üí ‚ÄúSignal messages and calls‚Äù), let‚Äôs say for a minute(s), hour, day, (for whatever reason), you certainly don‚Äôt want to be removed from all groups, otherwise you would have to join these groups again with a lot of effort.<br>\nb) but otherwise, imho, ‚ÄúDelete account‚Äù (Settings ‚Üí Account ‚Üí ‚ÄúDelete account‚Äù) should actually also revoke the group membership. (but not implemented so far, see Greyson‚Äôs reasoning)</p>",
