        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/teejay82/{size}/1806_2.png",
        "created_at": "2023-05-10T07:58:19.944Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I honestly don‚Äôt understand why a former Signal user should remain members of groups. It‚Äôs not like their group membership is reinstated once they join Signal again. I have experienced that with one of my contacts: they rejoined Signal, but didn‚Äôt automatically get added back into a group that I was the admin of. In fact, adding them back wasn‚Äôt exactly smooth, I only managed to get it to work by sending them a group link.</p>",
