        "created_at": "2023-05-10T13:40:25.568Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"TeeJay82\" data-post=\"7\" data-topic=\"53206\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/teejay82/48/1806_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> TeeJay82:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It‚Äôs not like their group membership is reinstated once they join Signal again.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>They could keep around a backup and restore it at a later point (assuming there are no incompatibilities with the current version of Signal), in which case you would expect group membership to be restored.</p>",
